title: Carson Palmer Retires; Black Monday Recap
itunes:title: Carson Palmer Retires; Black Monday Recap
description:
A room filled with some heroes- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler & Colleen Wolfe break the news about Carson Palmer’s retirement (00;00) and all the comings and goings of coaches including Bruce Arians (14;31), Jack Del Rio (24;47) and Vance Joseph staying in Denver (40;50). Finally, The Go get my Lunch standings are revealed (48;48) and much more!
